@page "/privacy-policy"

<PageTitle>Privacy Policy — PDFToolstack</PageTitle>

<div class="legal-page">
    <div class="legal-container">

        <div class="legal-header">
            <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
            <p class="legal-date">Last updated: March 22, 2026</p>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-content">

            <section class="legal-section">
                <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
                <p>
                    Welcome to PDFToolstack ("we," "our," or "us").
                    We are committed to protecting your personal
                    information and your right to privacy. This
                    Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use,
                    and safeguard your information when you visit
                    <strong>PDFToolstack.com</strong>.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="legal-section">
                <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
                <p>
                    We collect minimal information to provide our
                    services:
                </p>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Files you upload</strong> — PDF
                        files you upload for processing. These are
                        processed in memory and permanently deleted
                        within 1 hour. We never read, analyze, or
                        store the contents of your documents.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Usage data</strong> — Anonymous
                        information about how you use our tools,
                        including pages visited and tools used.
                        This data cannot identify you personally.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Cookies</strong> — Small files
                        stored on your device to remember your
                        theme preference and improve your
                        experience. See our Cookie Policy for
                        details.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Log data</strong> — Standard
                        server logs including IP address, browser
                        type, and pages visited. These are retained
                        for 30 days for security purposes.
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section class="legal-section">
                <h2>3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
                <p>We use the information we collect to:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        Process your PDF files and return results
                        to you
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Improve and optimize our tools and
                        services
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Monitor for abuse, fraud, and security
                        threats
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Display relevant advertisements through
                        Google AdSense
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Analyze usage patterns to add new features
                        our users need
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section class="legal-section">
                <h2>4. File Security and Deletion</h2>
                <p>
                    Your privacy is our top priority when it comes
                    to your documents:
                </p>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        All uploaded files are processed over an
                        encrypted HTTPS connection
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Files are processed in temporary memory
                        and not written to permanent storage
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Any temporary files are automatically
                        deleted within <strong>1 hour</strong>
                        of processing
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        We do not read, share, sell, or analyze
                        the contents of your documents
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Our staff cannot access your uploaded
                        files
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section class="legal-section">
                <h2>
                    5. Google AdSense and Third-Party Advertising
                </h2>
                <p>
                    We use Google AdSense to display advertisements
                    on our site. Google may use cookies and similar
                    technologies to serve ads based on your prior
                    visits to our site or other websites. You can
                    opt out of personalized advertising by visiting
                    <a href="https://www.google.com/settings/ads"
                       target="_blank" rel="noopener">
                        Google Ad Settings
                    </a>.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="legal-section">
                <h2>6. Cookies</h2>
                <p>We use the following types of cookies:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Essential cookies</strong> —
                        Required for the site to function
                        correctly
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Preference cookies</strong> —
                        Remember your theme selection and
                        settings
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Analytics cookies</strong> —
                        Help us understand how visitors use
                        our site
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Advertising cookies</strong> —
                        Used by Google AdSense to serve relevant
                        advertisements
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <p>
                    See our <a href="/cookie-policy">
                        Cookie Policy
                    </a> for full details.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="legal-section">
                <h2>7. Data Sharing</h2>
                <p>
                    We do not sell, trade, or rent your personal
                    information to third parties. We may share
                    anonymous, aggregated data with:
                </p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Google Analytics for usage analysis</li>
                    <li>
                        Google AdSense for advertisement
                        delivery
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Microsoft Azure for hosting and
                        infrastructure
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section class="legal-section">
                <h2>8. Your Rights</h2>
                <p>
                    Depending on your location, you may have the
                    following rights regarding your data:
                </p>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        The right to access data we hold about
                        you
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        The right to request deletion of your
                        data
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        The right to opt out of advertising
                        cookies
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        The right to lodge a complaint with a
                        supervisory authority
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <p>
                    To exercise any of these rights, please
                    contact us at
                    <a href="mailto:privacy@pdftoolstack.com">
                        privacy@pdftoolstack.com
                    </a>.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="legal-section">
                <h2>9. Children's Privacy</h2>
                <p>
                    PDFToolstack is not directed at children under
                    the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect
                    personal information from children. If you
                    believe a child has provided us with personal
                    information, please contact us immediately.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="legal-section">
                <h2>10. Changes to This Policy</h2>
                <p>
                    We may update this Privacy Policy from time to
                    time. We will notify you of any changes by
                    posting the new policy on this page and
                    updating the "Last updated" date. Your
                    continued use of our service after changes
                    constitutes acceptance of the updated
                    policy.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="legal-section">
                <h2>11. Contact Us</h2>
                <p>
                    If you have any questions about this Privacy
                    Policy, please contact us:
                </p>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        Email:
                        <a href="mailto:privacy@pdftoolstack.com">
                            privacy@pdftoolstack.com
                        </a>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Website:
                        <a href="/contact">
                            PDFToolstack.com/contact
                        </a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </section>

        </div>
    </div>
</div>